We've run into an issue where customers can respond to a "closed" ticket that is considered truely read-only.

When they respond to the ticket via email, it comments on the closed ticket rather than re-open a new one.

Can we please have the option to lock a ticket as read-only and have JSD create a new one regardless of the email chain designation?

